title: Iowa Team Time Trial State Championships
Iowa State Time Trial Championships
description: State of Iowa Time Trial Championships.  Nichols, IA  8/27/2006  Organized by the Iowa City Cycling Club, Iowa City, IA
course: Flat 20K and 40K out and back TT course on Hwy 70, south of Nichols, IA.  Start/fiinish is 1/2 mile south of town at county lot.  Turn-around is 10K and 20K south on Hwy 70.
registration: Registration is day of event at the start/finish, ending 15 minutes before the departure of the first rider at 8:00AM.  20 K riders first off, with riders started in order of registration.  USCF medals to top 3 Iowa riders in each catagory.
notes: Helmets required.  Equipment per USCF rules.  UCI rules do not apply.  USCF license required.  1 day lisenses available at registration.  Entry fee $15, all catagories except $5 Juniors.  Riders under 18 need parents signature.
directions: 1/4 mile south of Nichols, Iowa on Hwy 70.  Nichols is on Hwy 22 between Muscatine and Lone Tree.  Park in the DOT lot.
